- Kwereka abana ibintu babivuga mu mazina, kubavugisha, kuba- kinisha
  no kubaririmbira kenshi;
- Gukoresha igihe cyo kurya n’ibindi bikorwa byo mu rugo 
  bimwongerera kugirana ubusabane n’abo mu rugo;
- Guha abana urukundo no kubumva baba bishimye cyangwa 
  batishimye;
- Niba umwana agaragaza imikurire mibi cyangwa ate 
  ubumuga, hagomba kwitabwaho cyane ku bushobozi ate 
  ariko bakanamushishikariza gukora no gusabana n’abandi;
- Kudasiga umwana aryamye cyangwa yicaye mu gihe 
  cy’amasaha menshi;
- Gucunga umutekano w’aho umwana ari, kugira ngo atagira 
  impanuka; uvanaho ibintu bishobora kumukomeretsa cyangwa 
  ashobora gutamira;
- Gukomeza konsa umwana no kumuha indyo yuzuye kandi 
  ihagije;
- Kumenyereza umwana kumugaburira ukoresheje ikiyiko 
  n’igikombe;
- Kubahiriza no gukurikiza inkingo z’umwana;
- Kugirira umwana isuku kandi ukamumenyereza gukaraba intoki 
  n’amazi meza n’isabune.
